name: NVIDIA GEFORCE RTX 3090 Ti
description: The GeForce RTX 3090 Ti is an enthusiast-class graphics card by NVIDIA, launched on January 27th, 2022. Built on the 8 nm process, and based on the GA102 graphics processor, in its GA102-350-A1 variant, the card supports DirectX 12 Ultimate.
